<% const pageTitle = 'About RavindraStudio' %>
<div style="max-width:720px; margin:0 auto; padding:64px 24px 80px;">
    <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:56px;">
        <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--color-sage);">Our Story</span>
        <h1 style="font-size:2.6rem; margin-top:8px;">About RavindraStudio</h1>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--color-ink-soft); line-height:1.85;">
        <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">RavindraStudio is a small, independent frame shop — personally run, thoughtfully curated. Every frame in our collection is chosen for quality, craftsmanship, and the way it makes a photo feel like it truly belongs on a wall.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">We carry frames in every shape: the classic <strong>square</strong>, the elegant <strong>circle</strong>, the romantic <strong>heart</strong>, the timeless <strong>oval</strong>, and beyond — because memories aren't all the same shape, and neither should your frames be.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">All orders ship with careful packaging to make sure your frames arrive exactly as they left us. Cash on delivery and UPI are accepted — no pressure, no complex payment flows.</p>
        <p>Thank you for trusting RavindraStudio with your memories.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:48px; text-align:center;">
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn--primary">Shop All Frames</a>
    </div>
</div>

